25
0:01:19.72,000 --> 0:01:21,000
and move if we need to.

26
0:01:21.96,000 --> 0:01:23,000
But you can go back and push back on a student,

27
0:01:24.2,000 --> 0:01:27,000
and say, "Well, you know, you say that plants don't have brains,

28
0:01:27.28,000 --> 0:01:28,000
but plants do move."

29
0:01:28.76,000 --> 0:01:29,000
