147
0:06:35.08,000 --> 0:06:37,000
and so when it gets the first action potential,

148
0:06:37.32,000 --> 0:06:38,000
it starts counting, one, two,

149
0:06:38.76,000 --> 0:06:4,000
and if it gets to 20 and it doesn't fire again,

